-- Osborne Says Britain Is Ready to Give Support to Ireland Amid Bank Concern
-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 2010-11-17T08:01:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-17/osborne-says-britain-is-ready-to-give-support-to-ireland-amid-bank-concern.html
Britain stands ready to support
Ireland’s banking system, U.K. Chancellor of the Exchequer
George Osborne said.  “It’s in Britain’s national interest that the Irish
economy is successful and we have a stable banking system,”
Osborne told reporters before a meeting of European Union
finance ministers in Brussels today. “Britain stands ready to
support Ireland in the steps it needs to take.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Neuger at 
 jneuger@bloomberg.net  